The '''Razor Coast''' was a rocky shoreline on [[Jabiim/Legends|Jabiim]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] in the [[Battle of Jabiim]], it was the headquarters for [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederate]] forces under [[Alto Stratus]]. [[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi General]] [[Leska]]'s [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone trooper]] forces [[Battle of Razor Coast|captured]] the coast, but at a high rate of casualties.

